# Cloudflare Pages redirects.
#
# Note: the old SPA catch-all ("/* /index.html 200") is intentionally gone —
# Astro generates real pages for each route, so no client-side fallback is needed.
# Scanner-probe paths are handled by functions/_middleware.js (returns a real 404).

# Force oradiscuss.pages.dev visitors to the canonical production domain
https://oradiscuss.pages.dev/*      https://oradiscuss.com/:splat   301!
https://*.oradiscuss.pages.dev/*    https://oradiscuss.com/:splat   301!

# Canonicalise www.oradiscuss.com → oradiscuss.com (matches <link rel="canonical">)
https://www.oradiscuss.com/*        https://oradiscuss.com/:splat   301!
